n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lecongdanh\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/43b70e38edd5171cc5c7ae65585daf26?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/43b70e38edd5171cc5c7ae65585daf26?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lecongdanh\" class=\"reviewer-name\">lecongdanh</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">July 14, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This is the best plugin in the world</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Free Version is good - paid version not good</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/studentfilmmakers\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7ac07f611a2deb6e89bc984eafe23838?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7ac07f611a2deb6e89bc984eafe23838?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/studentfilmmakers\" class=\"reviewer-name\">StudentFilmmakers <small>(studentfilmmakers)</small></a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">July 11, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I had it set up free and thought I needed to just use the paid feature to add an IP to see what login and logout looked like so I got the paid version. However, when you load the paid version and the templates it removes the free templates and set\'s up a whole new workflow that includes building your template and saving it to a template file and then activating it. It put my site online so everyone can see it under construction and this it was not easy to get it back under construction. There was a bug that would not put my site back under the under construction. Finally went back to the free version and have not heard from support.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Semplice e completo</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/renzobassi\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b0985c1656ab63b7f0026c96296ac986?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b0985c1656ab63b7f0026c96296ac986?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/renzobassi\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Renzo Bassi <small>(renzobassi)</small></a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">June 17, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Molto semplice e veloce da attivare con una serie di template preimpostati anche nella versione free!!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good plugin but you need to upgrade for landing pages and coming soon pages,</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/karmikovic\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/54d5e84e95e73c3aaffbe59e3447edd8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/54d5e84e95e73c3aaffbe59e3447edd8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/karmikovic\" class=\"reviewer-name\">karmikovic</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">May 14, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Good plugin, but why the 2 star rating?  Here\'s a quote from the main summary of the plugin\n\n\"...Under Construction Page, Landing Page, Maintenance Mode &amp; Coming Soon WordPress plugin.\"\n\nWhats the problem?\n\nWell it should say \"Under construction preset pages, but upgrade to customize and then you can have Landing Page, Maintenance Mode &amp; Coming Soon\"\n\nThere you have it.  Not being honest especially about the main plugin header summary is a no no. \n\nIf you want a quick under construction page for free, try this plugin, but let me remind you, the actual page cannot be customized without an upgrade.\n\nVery good plugin otherwise, and I know the pro version would be really good, but I was looking for free solutions.  Peace.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Nice and effective!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ual1517\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cb9c1fdfa996273e1c742d25defb0cc3?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cb9c1fdfa996273e1c742d25defb0cc3?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ual1517\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ual1517</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">May 11, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Really easy to use.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Incredible customer support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nancybelinda\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0807d8f5a573c7060855eeea2bffbf67?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0807d8f5a573c7060855eeea2bffbf67?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nancybelinda\" class=\"reviewer-name\">nancybelinda</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">May 5, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I have a pro license and received incredible customer support - rapid response and solved all problems.  I wanted some customization and they offered to write some CSS to give me what I wanted.  Always pleasant.  My Under Construction page is beautiful and acts as a contact form until my site is fleshed out.  Thank you!!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simple</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/angelohigham\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8987062f379b67e0676f59c4b7d24996?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8987062f379b67e0676f59c4b7d24996?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/angelohigham\" class=\"reviewer-name\">angelohigham</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">March 15, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Simple to use.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Didn&#039;t uninstall on one site</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pickersmart\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/af38be81fe60d95424c56e443138d177?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/af38be81fe60d95424c56e443138d177?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pickersmart\" class=\"reviewer-name\">PickerSmart</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">January 24, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I uninstalled it on one of my sites under construction. I finished the work and turned it off but the under construction page was still there. I uninstalled the plugin and the under construction page was still there! I thought it might be a DNS Flush issue. So I removed it from 5 other site and they uninstalled ok. So I reinstalled it on the broken site thinking that maybe I didn\'t turn something off and it got stuck. I uninstalled one last time. It is still showing the under construction page! So I will see if I need to delete something in cPanel If that doesn\'t work I will reinstall word press. I wont be using this plugin again.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:109:\"Super-easy to use Under Construction Page, Landing Page, Maintenance Mode &amp; Coming Soon WordPress plugin.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:71:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/under-construction-page.3.50.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:39:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:76:\"https://ps.w.org/under-construction-page/assets/screenshot-1.gif?rev=1840052\";s:7:\"caption\";s:74:\"Build an under construction page in less than a minute with over 30 themes\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:76:\"https://ps.w.org/under-construction-page/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1840052\";s:7:\"caption\";s:29:\"Under Construction Text theme\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:76:\"https://ps.w.org/under-construction-page/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1840052\";s:7:\"caption\";s:18:\"Mad Designer theme\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:76:\"https://ps.w.org/under-construction-page/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=1840052\";s:7:\"caption\";s:16:\"Plain Text theme\";}i:5;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:76:\"https://ps.w.org/under-construction-page/assets/screenshot-5.png?rev=1840052\";s:7:\"caption\";s: