(4786, '_transient_yith_register_b9340c45f7c94928a9f4cdea1887a277', 'a:2:{s:6:\"Latest\";s:6:\"1.2.16\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:12291:\"\n        \n            <h4>Version 1.2.16 - Released on Aug 01, 2019</h4>\n        <ul>\n            <li>New: Support to WooCommerce 3.7 RC1</li>\n            <li>Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n            <li>Update: Italian language</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h4>Version 1.2.15 - Released on July 08, 2019 </h4>\n        <ul>\n        	<li> Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n        	<li> Fix: Small issue on admin area</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h4>Verson 1.2.14  - Released on July 03, 2019</h4>\n        <ul>\n        	<li>New: Custom email for Contact form tab available among WooCommerce Emails</li>\n			<li>Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n			<li>Update: Language files</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h4>Version 1.2.13 - Released on May 29, 2019</h4>\n        <ul>\n            <li>New: Support to WordPress 5.2</li>\n            <li>Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n            <li>Update: Spanish language</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h4>Version 1.2.12 - Released on Apr 03, 2019</h4>\n        <ul>\n        	<li>New:Support to WooCommerce 3.6 RC1</li>\n       		<li>New: Support to WordPress 5.1.1</li>\n			<li>Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n			<li>Fix: Issue with WPML</li>\n        </ul>\n          <h4>Version 1.2.11 - Released on Jan 23, 2019</h4>\n        <ul>\n        	<li>New:Support to WooCommerce 3.5.4</li>\n        	<li>Dev: Added ywtm_change_url_path</li>\n			<li>Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n        </ul>\n          <h4>Version 1.2.10 - Released on Jan 21, 2019</h4>\n        <ul>\n        	<li>Fix: Slash added to the download and FAQ tab</li>\n			<li>Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n        </ul>\n         <h4>Version 1.2.9 - Released on Dec 07, 2018</h4>\n        <ul>\n        	<li>New: Support to WordPress 5.0</li>\n			<li>Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n			<li>Update: WPML config file</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h4>Version 1.2.8 -